Well, that's because I stole something
from her... This, this! A bracelet!

511
00:54:37,990 --> 00:54:42,990
This is a cheap thing, but I stole it,
and that's why she kept following me.

512
00:54:45,900 --> 00:54:48,870
Hey, Go over there!

513
00:54:48,870 --> 00:54:52,870
I gave it back to you! Go!

514
00:54:55,670 --> 00:55:00,010
Why? I am your wife.

515
00:55:03,020 --> 00:55:04,880
Heol!

516
00:55:05,620 --> 00:55:07,890
This jerk!

517
00:55:10,890 --> 00:55:14,530
How dare you try to con us?

518
00:55:14,530 --> 00:55:18,530
No, the "wife" that she is
talking about doesn't mean that.

519
00:55:18,530 --> 00:55:20,300
Ah, I am celibate!

520
00:55:20,300 --> 00:55:22,630
I don't even know this girl's name. Seriously!

521
00:55:22,630 --> 00:55:26,640
Shut up! Just way one more word.
I'm going to just shoot!

522
00:55:26,640 --> 00:55:29,140
Yes, sir!

523
00:55:31,210 --> 00:55:34,750
Why are you saying useless things?
You should have left when I told you to go.

524
00:55:34,750 --> 00:55:36,950
What are you going to do now?

525
00:55:40,950 --> 00:55:44,120
Hey, why are you looking down there?

526
00:55:46,490 --> 00:55:51,460
I have a fear of heights and water.
It's better to just be shot at lightly—

527
00:55:51,460 --> 00:55:54,230
Being shot won't do. You will die like a dolphin.

528
00:55:54,230 --> 00:55:58,000
Of course. But I will die when I drown, too.

529
00:55:58,000 --> 00:56:01,270
Let me try to persuade them,
so you go first. Go first—

530
00:56:01,270 --> 00:56:03,440
Ahhh, okay, okay, okay. Wait a minute!

531
00:56:03,440 --> 00:56:07,650
Wait, wait, wait! What's wrong with you? Seriously?!

532
00:56:07,650 --> 00:56:09,380
Calm down! Calm.

533
00:56:23,630 --> 00:56:24,900
Shouldn't we catch them?

534
00:56:24,900 --> 00:56:26,530
Look for them!

