554
00:57:57,260 --> 00:58:01,290
♬ Your world, your heart ♬

555
00:58:01,290 --> 00:58:05,860
♬ Show them to me ♬

556
00:58:10,270 --> 00:58:12,700
Everything that got excavated from
the ocean is so amazing, right?

557
00:58:12,700 --> 00:58:16,210
Right. I hope to discover the wood panel quickly.

558
00:58:16,210 --> 00:58:20,580
The owner has a special eye for it.

559
00:58:20,580 --> 00:58:22,950
Totally my style.

560
