What is this?

561
00:58:31,560 --> 00:58:33,230
Huh?

562
00:58:33,230 --> 00:58:34,790
What is it?

563
00:58:37,230 --> 00:58:39,060
This picture.

564
00:58:49,670 --> 00:58:51,640
The Legend of the Blue Sea

565
00:58:51,640 --> 00:58:54,250
Which way to Seoul? Where is Seoul?

566
00:58:54,250 --> 00:58:56,050
I am not seducing you to go to Seoul.

567
00:58:56,050 --> 00:58:59,280
There are so many thing that
you would like in Seoul.

568
00:58:59,280 --> 00:59:00,250
Things like really
good specialty restaurants.

569
00:59:00,250 --> 00:59:01,890
Seoul seems big, right?

570
00:59:01,890 --> 00:59:03,820
It's as big as a palm.

571
00:59:03,820 --> 00:59:07,930
As one lives, everyone crosses
paths briefly by chance sometime.

572
00:59:07,930 --> 00:59:10,560
It's just that people don't know that fact.
